39f68186-c076-4c3a-95c3-5459b4c1d9d4.do_description: To make the output, you have to...change all patterns of two grey blocks to red, change all patterns of 9 grey blocks to blue, and fill in all other grey blocks with black.
39f68186-c076-4c3a-95c3-5459b4c1d9d4.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same
39f68186-c076-4c3a-95c3-5459b4c1d9d4.see_description: In the input, you should see...several patterns of grey blocks.

62518520-7fa6-42fa-aa4c-0d7a5bb6b5c8.do_description: To make the output, you have to... copy the input grid and color the long shape with blue and the short with red.
62518520-7fa6-42fa-aa4c-0d7a5bb6b5c8.grid_description: The output grid size... same as the input grid.
62518520-7fa6-42fa-aa4c-0d7a5bb6b5c8.see_description: In the input, you should see... the long shape and short shape.

773f5f62-5ca2-4d06-ac7e-b8932300d2fb.do_description: To make the output, you have to...change the shortest colored blocks from gray to red and the tallest colored blocks from gray to blue. Change the remaining gray blocks to black.
773f5f62-5ca2-4d06-ac7e-b8932300d2fb.grid_description: The output grid size...will remain the same.
773f5f62-5ca2-4d06-ac7e-b8932300d2fb.see_description: In the input, you should see...only vertical blocks which stay on rows 1, 3, 5, 7 and 9.

7a261c75-69b4-44e0-855f-7aeccb520883.do_description: To make the output, you have to...change the shortest group of blocks from gray to red, change the tallest group of blocks from gray to blue. Change the remaining gray blocks to black.
7a261c75-69b4-44e0-855f-7aeccb520883.grid_description: The output grid size...will remain the same.
7a261c75-69b4-44e0-855f-7aeccb520883.see_description: In the input, you should see...blocks that only go vertically.

f1a3307d-a9c3-45a2-87d1-94a6dafe0244.do_description: To make the output, you have to... change the shortest grey line to red and the tallest line to blue. The remaining lines turn black.
f1a3307d-a9c3-45a2-87d1-94a6dafe0244.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input
f1a3307d-a9c3-45a2-87d1-94a6dafe0244.see_description: In the input, you should see... grey vertical lines.
